Unconstructed drawstring pouches and shoulder bags come painted or embroidered with flowers #ETROliveshow #MFW #ETRO
The colour palette moves from ivory to muted pinks, apricot and mauve, to taupe, black and midnight blue #ETROliveshow #MFW #ETRO
The elaborate, yet functional details of a dancer’s wardrobe make their way onto flat, easy footwear #ETROliveshow #MFW #ETRO
The focus is on sleeves: embellished or fluttering with layers of lace and tied with thin ribbons #ETROliveshow #MFW #ETRO
Floral embroideries are hand-stitched on silk tulle, creating a whispering, feminine tattoo effect #ETROliveshow #MFW #ETRO
Bomber jackets with ribbons and silk georgette jogging pants cut the romanticism with an edge #ETROliveshow #MFW #ETRO
Ribbons run throughout the collection  enhancing a feminine allure #ETROliveshow #MFW #ETRO
Fluent silhouettes and wrap-like constructions follow the movement of the body #ETROliveshow #MFW #ETRO
Fabrics are elaborate and rich, yet frayed and imperfect to create a relaxed attitude #ETROliveshow #MFW #ETRO
Long fluid reversible silk robes, plissé skirts and fluttering dresses float with a dance-like, summery ease #ETROliveshow #MFW #ETRO
The graceful world of ballet informs the muted palette of dusty roses #ETROliveshow #MFW #ETRO
The bohemian craft of South of France meets the exquisite workmanship of antique clothing from Eastern Europe #ETROliveshow #MFW #ETRO
The collection scatters fresh seeds, blooming a springtime #ETROliveshow #MFW #ETRO
